name: The Invisible Woman
description:
"The Invisible Woman" by BryantW

The innocent are always invisible until the horror unfolds around us. Dont let history make you invisible stand up and fight back. 

This artwork was created using old public domain illustrations collage together and remixed with patterns and other effects in Photoshop.

5120px x 5120px .jpg - Date of completion 3/14/2022

About the artist - Bryant W. is a broken child born of the 80’s using his artistic skills to help the world find beauty within the ugliness that surrounds us all.
